---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service — Far Fox" description="Far Fox terms of service. The rules of the road for using our couples app.">
  <nav class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 backdrop-blur-md bg-fox-bg/80 border-b border-fox-pink/10">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <img src="/fox-logo.png" alt="Far Fox" class="w-8 h-8" />
        <span class="text-xl font-900 tracking-tight bg-gradient-to-r from-fox-pink to-fox-purple bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          Far Fox
        </span>
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://app.lovefarfox.com"
        class="px-5 py-2 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-fox-pink to-fox-purple text-white font-700 text-sm hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-fox-pink/25 transition-all duration-200 hover:-translate-y-0.5"
      >
        Open App
      </a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="pt-28 pb-24 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-900 tracking-tight mb-8">
        Terms of <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-fox-pink to-fox-purple bg-clip-text text-transparent">Service</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-fox-text-light text-sm mb-8">Last updated: March 30, 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-8 text-fox-text-light leading-relaxed">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-800 text-fox-text mb-3">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p>
            By creating an account or using Far Fox, you agree to these terms of service. If you do not agree, please do not use the app.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-800 text-fox-text mb-3">2. Description of Service</h2>
          <p>
            Far Fox is a couples app designed for long-distance relationships. It provides features including shared photos, love letters, daily questions, mood tracking, challenges, and a virtual fox companion. The service is available via web browser and mobile devices.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-800 text-fox-text mb-3">3. Account Registration</h2>
          <p>You must provide accurate information when creating your account. You are responsible for:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>Keeping your login credentials secure.</li>
            <li>All activity that occurs under your account.</li>
            <li>Notifying us immediately of unauthorized access.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-800 text-fox-text mb-3">4. Acceptable Use</h2>
          <p>You agree not to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>Use the app for any unlawful purpose.</li>
            <li>Upload content that is abusive, harmful, or violates another person's rights.</li>
            <li>Attempt to access another user's account or data.</li>
            <li>Reverse engineer, decompile, or disassemble the app.</li>
            <li>Use automated tools to access the service without permission.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-800 text-fox-text mb-3">5. Your Content</h2>
          <p>
            You retain ownership of all content you create in Far Fox (photos, letters, question answers, etc.). By using the app, you grant us a limited license to store, process, and display your content to your connected partner as part of the service.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-800 text-fox-text mb-3">6. Partner Connection</h2>
          <p>
            Far Fox is designed for use between two connected partners. Content you share is visible to your connected partner. You are responsible for the content you share. Disconnecting from a partner may result in the removal of shared content.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-800 text-fox-text mb-3">7. Service Availability</h2>
          <p>
            We strive to keep Far Fox available at all times, but we do not guarantee uninterrupted service. We may perform maintenance, updates, or experience outages. We are not liable for any loss resulting from service interruptions.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-800 text-fox-text mb-3">8. Termination</h2>
          <p>
            You may delete your account at any time. We may suspend or terminate your account if you violate these terms. Upon termination, your data will be deleted in accordance with our <a href="/privacy" class="text-fox-pink hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-800 text-fox-text mb-3">9. Disclaimer</h2>
          <p>
            Far Fox is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. We do not guarantee that the app will meet your expectations, be error-free, or that any defects will be corrected.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-800 text-fox-text mb-3">10. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>
            To the fullest extent permitted by law, Far Fox shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising from your use of the app.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-800 text-fox-text mb-3">11. Changes to Terms</h2>
          <p>
            We may update these terms from time to time. Continued use of the app after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-800 text-fox-text mb-3">12. Contact</h2>
          <p>
            Questions about these terms? Reach out at
            <a href="mailto:hello@lovefarfox.com" class="text-fox-pink hover:underline">hello@lovefarfox.com</a>.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="py-12 px-6 border-t border-fox-pink/10">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
      <span class="font-800 text-lg bg-gradient-to-r from-fox-pink to-fox-purple bg-clip-text text-transparent">Far Fox</span>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-sm text-fox-text-light/50">
        <a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-fox-pink transition-colors">Privacy</a>
        <a href="/terms" class="hover:text-fox-pink transition-colors">Terms</a>
        <span>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Far Fox</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
